column3: the first applebees event, we did fun things and everyone met for the first time in hoes and joes

Phillip, Shawn, Edric, and Jon were in Brooklyn, New York City. Due to the circumstances, the atmosphere and vibe of the group was grim. Phill, deciding to be a total genius decides to buy a can of GOYA Baked Beans. And eat them straight out of the fucking can with a plastic spoon. He then shared it with us. The fucking beans man. They were beautiful. TAGS: NYC, bean, phill moment
